  <Docs>
    <summary>
    A class for manual interaction with the RUM feature. It records RUM events that are sent to Datadog RUM.
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>There can be only one active RUM monitor for certain instance of Datadog SDK. It gets enabled along with 
      the call to <c>DDRUM.Enable (DDRUMConfiguration configuration)</c>:</para>
      <para>
        <c>
          // Enable RUM feature:
          RUM.Enable (DDRUMConfiguration configuration)

          // Use RUM monitor:
          DDRUMMonitor.Shared.StartView(...)
        </c>
    </para>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
